long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
TikTok All Liked Videos Remover is a powerful Chrome extension designed to simplify the process of removing all liked videos on TikTok. With just a click of a button, this extension enables you to effortlessly dislike your entire collection of liked videos on TikTok.

Are you looking to start fresh on TikTok or simply want to clear out your liked videos? TikTok All Liked Videos Remover provides a convenient solution. No more spending hours manually disliking videos one by one. This extension automates the process, saving you valuable time and effort.

To use the extension, ensure that you are logged in to your TikTok account and on your profile page. Simply click the "Start" button provided by the extension, and it will initiate the automatic removal of your liked videos. Each video will be disliked at intervals of 3 seconds, ensuring a smooth and efficient process.
